# fsw-symbol

The fsw-symbol component can be used to create a symbol image

## fsw-symbol
<fsw-symbol symbol="S10000"></fsw-symbol>

    <fsw-symbol symbol="S10000"></fsw-symbol>

## fsw-symbol with style string
<fsw-symbol symbol="S10020" styling="-CZ2"></fsw-symbol>

    <fsw-symbol symbol="S10020" styling="-CZ2"></fsw-symbol>
